		{"id":"be_state","type":"text","text":"**State Manager**\n`Backend/api/state.py`\n\n- Global Singleton `STATE`\n- UI Events Queue\n- Session Usage Stats\n- Download Tasks Status","x":-1120,"y":-310,"width":280,"height":210,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"lk_worker","type":"text","text":"**Voice Agent Worker**\n`Backend/livekit/worker.py`\n\n- VAD (Silero)\n- STT (Whisper/Deepgram)\n- TTS (Piper/Silero/OpenAI)\n- LLM (WakeWordWrapper)","x":-1180,"y":-1080,"width":280,"height":240,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"lk_server","type":"text","text":"**LiveKit Server**\n(External Binary)\n\n- WebRTC SFU\n- Audio/Video Routing","x":-1180,"y":-1460,"width":260,"height":160,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"be_tools","type":"text","text":"**Core Plugins Loader**\n`Backend/plugins/plugin_loader.py`\n\n- Loads `tools`, `snapshots`, `watchers`\n- Manages dependencies\n- Validates manifests","x":-1120,"y":425,"width":360,"height":185,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"be_logic","type":"text","text":"**Chat Processing Logic**\n`_unified_chat_processing_stream`\n\n1. Wait for Snapshot\n2. Load Settings & Profile\n3. Fetch Activity & Chat History\n4. Build Context (Raw + Summary)\n5. Select Tools (Core + MCP)\n6. Create LangChain Agent\n7. Stream Execution","x":-670,"y":105,"width":345,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"be_routers","type":"text","text":"**API Routers**\n`Backend/api/`\n\n- `chat_router.py`: Chat endpoints\n- `settings_router.py`: Config mgmt\n- `state_router.py`: UI state/events","x":-1120,"y":-40,"width":360,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"db_sqlite","type":"text","text":"**SQLite Database**\n`Backend/db.sqlite`\n\n- `message_store`: Chat history\n- `chat_summary_chunks`: Episodic chat\n- `activity_summary_chunks`: Episodic activity\n- `usage_stats`: Token usage/cost","x":404,"y":-135,"width":393,"height":240,"color":"5"},
